{"title":"Chris King Announces Micro Spline for R45D Hubs","link":"https://theradavist.com/chris-king-micro-spline-r45d-hubs/","date":1704382042000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-2-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1ee84457-7e2e-498d-87ed-ecb578e5c230&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fchrisking.com%2Fproducts%2Fr45d-micro-spline-conversion-kit\" target=\"_blank\">Chris King</a> has announced the release of new Micro Spline drivers for their market-leading R45D hubs, available January 1st from all Chris King retailers. Check out all the info below!</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/MS-R45D-3-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Shimano’s Micro Spline technology improves engagement in the freehub, with 23 closely spaced splines driving the cassette. Coupled with Chris King’s own R45D hubs, which take a similar approach to consistent engagement, the new Micro Spline drivers produce an unparalleled ride experience.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/r45d-ms-4x5-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/r45d-ms-4x5-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/r45d-ms-4x5-1.jpg?resize=1024,819&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/r45d-ms-4x5-1.jpg?resize=768,614&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/r45d-ms-4x5-1.jpg?resize=1800,1440&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/r45d-ms-4x5-1.jpg?resize=1335,1068&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/r45d-ms-4x5-1.jpg?resize=700,560&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/01/r45d-ms-4x5-1.jpg?resize=1536,1229&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>The new drivers are compatible with all King Centerlock and 6-bolt (Gen 2) R45D hubs, which already support Shimano HG EV along with SRAM XDR systems. King’s Micro Spline drivers will be available in silver and black.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with all centerlock R45D versions and Gen. 2 6-bolt hubs, including those with serial numbers starting at 691XXXXX.</li>\n<li>Compatible with Mountain cassettes. Utilizes Shimano’s wide range cassettes for gravel use and the 23 splines.</li>\n<li>With this addition, R45D hubs are compatible with Shimano HG, XD/XDR, and Micro Spline 12.</li>\n<li>Available in black and silver</li>\n<li>$250 USD</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1ee84457-7e2e-498d-87ed-ecb578e5c230&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fchrisking.com%2Fproducts%2Fr45d-micro-spline-conversion-kit\" target=\"_blank\">Chris King</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/chris-king-micro-spline-r45d-hubs/\">Chris King Announces Micro Spline for R45D Hubs</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"a2bbb2de3f753453efe10281263c534463cab1bf2ca21e3492d2bfee110b5a8a","category":"Cycling"}